N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22ยง 26.4 - Request for information regarding filed statements

State Regulations
A request for information regarding a filed statement
must be made, in writing, to the Office of Court Administration, Appointment

Processing Unit, 25 Beaver Street, 8th Floor, New York, New York 10004 or via
email to part36@nycourts.gov, specifying the information
desired. Notes
